						               													<description>Numeracy Legends and The Rainbow Unicorn is a resource allocation and route arrangement game. Originating from the math puzzle Seven Bridges of K&amp;ouml;nigsberg, this game creates a challenge of observation and abstract thinking, where players are required to plan the most efficient route to win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Three brief steps of the rules:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Step 1. Set up the map with food ingredients and transportation, then choose any food spot as a starting point. The goal is to be the first to collect enough ingredients to make a cupcake.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Step 2. Players can either move along the roads by paying transportation, or stay and supply more transportation.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Step 3. Reach the magic circle after successfully collecting enough numbers of ingredients. Note that a same type of ingredient cannot be collected twice.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;--&amp;#10;Other games from Numeracy Legends Trilogy:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Numeracy Legends and The Zerda Fox&amp;#10;https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/224749/numeracy-legends-and-zerda-fox&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Numeracy Legends and The Gluttony Dragon&amp;#10;https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/224750/numeracy-legends-and-gluttony-dragon&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
